						<summary>

						<p>Stone lying in the bastion.</p>						

						<p>This undated inscription may be assigned to the 8th century A.D., on the basis of palaeography.</p>						

						<p>Fragment. It seems to record a gift of <hi rend="italic">Pannavija</hi> (or Pannavisa) for the maintenance of a lamp at the village Chirīkura of Renāṇḍu.</p>						

						</summary>
